BBNaija ex-housemate, Bright O has broken his silence on the ‘blow job’ saga with his fellow housemate, Dorathy. This comes after Dorathy eventually opened up during the reunion show on Tuesday, 22nd of June that she gave Bright O a blow job only for him to ignore her the next day. Taking to social media to address the issue, Lord B as he is also called, said the reason why he ignored Dorathy afterwards was because his manhood became swollen after the act. Brighto wrote: “She gave me a blow job and the next morning I had a swollen D*ck, I gaz japa.Face with cold sweat …. #BBNaijaReunion … #BBNaijaReunion lordb.”